    <item>
      <title>瑞士股市 13 个月内第二次停电，停市数小时</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/swiss-stock-exchange-trading-halted-due-to-technical-issues</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士证券市场运营商周三因技术故障无法发布定价数据而暂停股票交易数小时，这是该交易所有史以来最长的宕机，也是一年多以来第二次宕机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/swiss-stock-exchange-trading-halted-due-to-technical-issues</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 08:13:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
